OL,3,CArrest after man found unconscious in
OL,4,Cpark dies
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder following the death of a man
OL,8,Ffound unconscious in a park, police
OL,9,Fhave said.
OL,11,FLeicestershire Police confirmed the 62-
OL,12,Fyear-old victim died in hospital after
OL,13,Fbeing discovered in the park in
OL,14,FLeicester on Monday.
OL,16,FA 33-year-old man was arrested and
OL,17,Fremains in police custody.
