SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775667952
OL,3,CArrest after man found unconscious in
OL,4,Cpark dies
OL,6,FPolice said East Midlands Ambulance
OL,7,FService was called to Beaumont Park
OL,8,Fjust before 7pm. An area between
OL,9,FKrefeld Way and Beaumont Way was
OL,10,Fcordoned off for officers to examine
OL,11,Fthe scene.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Kevin Hames, from
OL,14,FEast Midlands Murder Investigation
OL,15,FTeam, said house-to-house enquiries
OL,16,Fand studies of CCTV were taking place.
OL,18,FHe said: "We are in the very early
OL,19,Fstages of our investigation into the
OL,20,Fincident and the events leading up to
OL,21,Fit.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
