OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775667952
OL,3,CArrest after man found unconscious in
OL,4,Cpark dies
OL,6,F"The victim's family have been
OL,7,Fidentified and are being supported by
OL,8,Fspecialist officers through this
OL,9,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,11,F"We would urge anyone who was in this
OL,12,Farea during the evening and may have
OL,13,Fwitnessed what happened or have any
OL,14,Finformation about the incident to get
OL,15,Fin touch. We know it's not always easy
OL,16,Fto report what you may have seen or
OL,17,Fheard but it's vitally important we
OL,18,Fspeak to as many people as possible."
